plot: A high school group 'Sket-Dan' (Helper Group) is dedicated to helping students and staff alike with literally any problem they may have. Partly due to this ambiguity and strange set of individuals in the group, they are often looked down upon but regardless, the three members will enthusiastically do anything to complete the jobs presented to them.   Written by  Mattias1
